  "detailed_description": "WAIFU IMPACT 2 is a third person shooter, adventure game with role-playing elements where you explore the Waifu Islands to unlock new characters and abilities.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE THE WAIFU ISLANDS</h2><br>In WAIFU IMPACT 2 there are different islands to explore. Each island has a different climate and different enemies. Discover all the secrets that await you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/909c01931e17438124c6ae5405bc9bb0.poster.avif?t=1731070157\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/909c01931e17438124c6ae5405bc9bb0.webm?t=1731070157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/909c01931e17438124c6ae5405bc9bb0.mp4?t=1731070157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SAVE THE WAIFUS WITH THE POWER OF THE CRYSTALS</h2><br>Find crystal shards to release the waifus from their crystal prison. Every island has a different waifu you must save.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/01d8ddbcc5f2f3abb839b286218a8f01.poster.avif?t=1731070157\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/01d8ddbcc5f2f3abb839b286218a8f01.webm?t=1731070157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/01d8ddbcc5f2f3abb839b286218a8f01.mp4?t=1731070157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVEL UP YOUR WAIFUS</h2><br>Defeat enemies with your favourite waifu to level up her affinity for you. Level her enough and unlock powerful abilities and new images from the gallery.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/7cb2355badae7c2bfdb8f5454cfd2315.avif?t=1731070157\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER THE SECRETS</h2><br>The Waifu Islands hide many secrets, like hidden chests or puzzles. If you solve them you will obtain lots of crystals to save the waifus.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/461b49dd0d8b7f433a24b5c9d0ebe3ac.avif?t=1731070157\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHANGE YOUR OUTFIT</h2><br>You will also unlock different outfits for your waifus. Find the one that suits your mood the most!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/f905e67deb57d1b856e68734e3132da9.avif?t=1731070157\" width=500 height=280 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "WAIFU IMPACT 2 is a third person shooter, adventure game with role-playing elements where you explore the Waifu Islands to unlock new characters and abilities.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE THE WAIFU ISLANDS</h2><br>In WAIFU IMPACT 2 there are different islands to explore. Each island has a different climate and different enemies. Discover all the secrets that await you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/909c01931e17438124c6ae5405bc9bb0.poster.avif?t=1731070157\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/909c01931e17438124c6ae5405bc9bb0.webm?t=1731070157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/909c01931e17438124c6ae5405bc9bb0.mp4?t=1731070157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SAVE THE WAIFUS WITH THE POWER OF THE CRYSTALS</h2><br>Find crystal shards to release the waifus from their crystal prison. Every island has a different waifu you must save.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/01d8ddbcc5f2f3abb839b286218a8f01.poster.avif?t=1731070157\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/01d8ddbcc5f2f3abb839b286218a8f01.webm?t=1731070157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/01d8ddbcc5f2f3abb839b286218a8f01.mp4?t=1731070157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVEL UP YOUR WAIFUS</h2><br>Defeat enemies with your favourite waifu to level up her affinity for you. Level her enough and unlock powerful abilities and new images from the gallery.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/7cb2355badae7c2bfdb8f5454cfd2315.avif?t=1731070157\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER THE SECRETS</h2><br>The Waifu Islands hide many secrets, like hidden chests or puzzles. If you solve them you will obtain lots of crystals to save the waifus.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/461b49dd0d8b7f433a24b5c9d0ebe3ac.avif?t=1731070157\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHANGE YOUR OUTFIT</h2><br>You will also unlock different outfits for your waifus. Find the one that suits your mood the most!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989870/extras/f905e67deb57d1b856e68734e3132da9.avif?t=1731070157\" width=500 height=280 /></span>",
